03:33.200 --> 03:35.120
Yeah, it's good that they finally sorted that out.

03:35.120 --> 03:38.880
They sorted out a while back, but now we've got a proper release with it.

03:38.880 --> 03:41.220
Hopefully we can just put that stuff behind us now.

03:41.220 --> 03:45.800
