14:14.880 --> 14:15.880
to his system alone.

14:15.880 --> 14:19.960
Yeah, and he said that there have been hundreds to date because we speculated there were only

14:19.960 --> 14:20.960
a few, as you say.

14:20.960 --> 14:22.240
But no, there have been hundreds.

14:22.240 --> 14:24.320
Yeah, it's fascinating the way this system works.

14:24.320 --> 14:25.320
And I was confused.

14:25.320 --> 14:26.520
It's like, how are you doing this?

14:26.520 --> 14:28.640
